<h1><span id="London_System">London System</span></h1>
<h3><span id="3._Bf4.2C_London_System"></span><span id="3._Bf4,_London_System">3. Bf4, London System</span></h3>
<p>In the London System, White puts his pawns on e3 and c3, but only after developing his dark-square bishop, to avoid blocking it in.
</p>
<p><b>1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 e6 3. Bf4</b>
</p>
